[@slide title glow] Falling Star
[@subtitle] A starry-night theme — gold on deep indigo, with a shooting star

[statement kicker:"same engine, new sky"]
A theme is just [text color:accent weight:bold]data and one CSS file[/text].
[/statement]

[@slide] Choices — cards
[@subtitle] One option per card

[cards cols:3]
  [card icon:cube title:Tokens] Data, validated against a schema. [/card]
  [card icon:star title:Components state:win pill:Core animated] Manifest + template + CSS. [/card]
  [card icon:swatch title:Themes] A value-set each, light & dark. [/card]
[/cards]

[@slide] By the numbers
[@subtitle] Glass tiles floating over the night

[scorecard]
  [kpi value:45 label:Components change:"+10" dir:up]
  [kpi value:2 label:Themes change:"+1" dir:up]
  [kpi value:0 label:Dependencies]
[/scorecard]

[callout tone:tip] The shooting star streaks across whichever slide is on screen. [/callout]

